HEADWORD: Proverbially
<hw>Pro*ver"bi*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a proverbial manner;
by way of proverb; hence, commonly; universally; <as>as, it is
<ex>proverbially</ex> said; the bee is <ex>proverbially</ex>
busy.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

